dct_title_s: Plan von Wien = Plan of Vienna = Plan de Vienne = Pianta di Vienna
dct_description_sm: Kartographische Anstalt Freytag-Berndt u. Artaria Freytag-Berndt u. Artaria. In upper left margin: Freytag-Berndt Stadtplan. In lower left corner of map: "096-68." Legend in German, English, French and Italian. Bezirke, administrative districts, are listed and located. Map Library does not have the street index accompanying this map.
